<h1>Welcome to NduthiRide! 🎉</h1>
<p>Hi <strong style="color:#F0F0F0;">{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>
  Your account has been created successfully. You can now book fast, safe boda boda rides
  and same-day parcel deliveries across Nairobi.
</p>

{{#if email}}
<div class="alert">
  <strong>Verify your email</strong> — we sent a separate OTP to this address to confirm
  your email. You can still use the app while unverified.
</div>
{{/if}}

<hr class="divider" />

<h2>What you can do</h2>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">🏍 Book a Ride</span>
  <span class="info-value">Instant boda pickup</span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">📦 Send a Parcel</span>
  <span class="info-value">Same-day delivery</span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">💬 In-app Chat</span>
  <span class="info-value">Talk to your rider</span>
</div>
<div class="info-row">
  <span class="info-label">📍 Live Tracking</span>
  <span class="info-value">See your rider on the map</span>
</div>

<hr class="divider" />

<p style="text-align:center;">
  <a href="{{appUrl}}" class="btn">Open NduthiRide</a>
</p>

<p style="font-size:13px; color:#555; text-align:center; margin-top:16px;">
  Questions? Reply to this email or contact us at
  <a href="mailto:support@nduthiride.co.ke">support@nduthiride.co.ke</a>
</p>
